data.description: Welcome to this truly exceptional desert property located on 1.25 acres, including a 400 Sq.ft. guest home that is sure to captivate your senses. One of the outstanding features of this property is the two rooftop solar arrays that produce 8.525KW. Step inside and be amazed by the newly remodeled kitchen, where culinary dreams come true. Equipped with a top-of-the-line Bosch dishwasher. The elegant quartz countertops add a touch of sophistication to the space, while the upgraded electrical and plumbing ensure modern functionality and reliability. A large double sink is perfect for handling various kitchen tasks with ease. The bathroom is also a luxurious retreat, featuring a freestanding soaking tub that invites you to unwind and relax after a long day. A striking five-foot shower enclosed in  glass awaits, complete with a rainfall shower head for an invigorating experience. To add a touch of modernity and comfort, a bidet is also included, enhancing your daily routine. The large mirror, complemented by adjustable LED illumination, ensures you have the perfect lighting for any occasion. Throughout the property, you'll find thoughtfully designed and carefully selected reclaimed barn wood accent walls, providing a rustic yet chic ambiance to the newly remodeled hallway and bedrooms. Embrace the warmth and character that this design element brings to the living spaces. As you step outside, The natural beauty of the surrounding landscape creates a sense of tranquility, making it a perfect place to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life, Adding to the allure of the property is the Cowboy pool. taking a dip in the pool during these hot desert days, surrounded by the vast beauty of nature. It's the ideal spot for relaxation. Property also includes this charming and self-contained guest home. Let's explore the captivating features that make this guest home a true gem. Once inside, you'll notice the thoughtful design and attention to detail. The guest home is equipped with a mini-split system, Dual pane windows, Reclaimed barn wood accent walls that continue to be a prominent and charming feature in the guest home with The natural beauty of the barn wood that adds character and warmth to the space, making it a perfect retreat to unwind and relax.   With its own set of amenities and thoughtful design, this guest home provides a private and welcoming space  and includes it's own private patio. See this one of a kind home for yourself today before it's gone.
